<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Java Developer Experience</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        .company {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .company h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .company p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Java Developer Work Experience: "${companyStatus}"</h1>

        <div class="company">
            <h2>1. Tech Solutions Inc.</h2>
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> Junior Java Developer</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Jan 2021 - Dec 2021</p>
            <p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Developed and maintained Java-based web applications.</li>
                <li>Worked with Spring Boot to build RESTful APIs.</li>
                <li>Collaborated with the front-end team to integrate APIs.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="company">
            <h2>2. CodeCraft Ltd.</h2>
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> Mid-Level Java Developer</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Jan 2022 - Present</p>
            <p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Led the migration of legacy systems to Spring Boot.</li>
                <li>Implemented Hibernate for efficient database management.</li>
                <li>Optimized application performance and conducted code reviews.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="company">
            <h2>3. FutureTech Innovations</h2>
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> Freelance Java Developer</p>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> Ongoing</p>
            <p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Developing custom Java applications for various clients.</li>
                <li>Integrating MySQL databases using JDBC.</li>
                <li>Providing technical support and documentation.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
